text: Novovochepshy () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Vochepshiyskoye Rural Settlement of Teuchezhsky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 169 as of 2018. There are 2 streets. == Ethnicity == The khutor is inhabited by Adighes. == References == Category:Rural localities in Teuchezhsky District
title: Novovochepshy
